metrics.visualTitle: Sum of Coffee, green Production ( tonnes) by Entity

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'world food production'[Entity],
			"SumCoffee__green_Production___tonnes_", CALCULATE(SUM('world food production'[Coffee, green Production ( tonnes)]))
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(
			1001,
			__DS0Core,
			[SumCoffee__green_Production___tonnes_],
			0,
			'world food production'[Entity],
			1
		)

EVALUATE
	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
	[SumCoffee__green_Production___tonnes_] DESC, 'world food production'[Entity]

metrics.visualTitle: Sum of Wheat ,Maize and Rice Production (tonnes) by Year

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'world food production'[Year],
			"SumWheat_Production__tonnes_", CALCULATE(SUM('world food production'[Wheat Production (tonnes)])),
			"SumMaize_Production__tonnes_", CALCULATE(SUM('world food production'[Maize Production (tonnes)])),
			"SumRice__Production___tonnes_", CALCULATE(SUM('world food production'[Rice  Production ( tonnes)]))
		)

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

	VAR __DS0BodyBinnedSample = 
		SAMPLEAXISWITHLOCALMINMAX(
			3500,
			__DS0Core,
			'world food production'[Year],
			[SumWheat_Production__tonnes_],
			[SumMaize_Production__tonnes_],
			[SumRice__Production___tonnes_],
			350,
			,
			ALPHABETICAL,
			ASC,
			105000,
			60
		)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
	"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount
)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyBinnedSample

ORDER BY
	'world food production'[Year]
